ecr2 2.1.0
========

* Added: uniform crossover recombinator recUnifCrossover
* Added: parameter log.stats for ecr function (possibility to define fitness statistics to be logged)
* Added: logical log.pop argument for ecr function (should each population be saved in the logger?)

ecr2 2.0
=========

* First submission of ecr 2 to CRAN.
* Almost everything changed.
